      </p></div><div><p><em><a title="Games > Borderlands 4 [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/borderlands-4">Borderlands 4</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,320 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,859 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,174 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, and <em><a title="Games > Dragon Ball: Gekishin Squadra [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dragon-ball-gekishin-squadra">Dragon Ball: Gekishin Squadra</a></em> for PlayStation 5, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,321 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,629 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, PC, iOS, and Android&nbsp;are the highlights of this week’s Japanese video game releases. <span id="more-990365"></span></p><p>Also due out this week are <em><a title="Games > The Little Tomb: The Maholova Club and the Search for a Dead Body [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/the-little-tomb-the-maholova-club-and-the-search-for-a-dead-body">The Little Tomb: The Maholova Club and the Search for a Dead Body</a></em> for PC, the PlayStation 4 version of&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Marvel Rivals [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/marvel-rivals">Marvel Rivals</a></em>, and <em><a title="Games > Roman Sands RE:Build [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/roman-sands-re-build">Roman Sands RE:Build</a></em> for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, PlayStation 4, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,167 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, Switch, and PC.</p><p>Get the full list of this week’s Japanese game releases below. It should be noted that <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https: