ries-from-sol-the-gun-dog-multi-language/13/70in0j?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>) – Already available worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > SunnySide [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/sunnyside">SunnySide</a></em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/sunnyside-multi-language/13/70iod3?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>) – Already available worldwide.</li></ul><h2><span>Digital Only</span></h2><ul><li><em>Borderlands 4</em> (Xbox Series, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1285190/Borderlands_4/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/borderlands-4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/bubsy-in-the-purrfect-collection">Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3039890/Bubsy_in_The_Purrfect_Collection/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Call of the Sea</em> (Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > CAPTURED [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/captured">CAPTURED</a></em> (PS5) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Dragon Ball: Gekishin Squadra</em> (PS5, PS4, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10007638" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>], iOS, Android) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Gloomy Eyes [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/gloomy-eyes">Gloomy Eyes</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2667950/Gloomy_Eyes__The_Game/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > KARMA: The Dark World [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/karma-the-dark-world">KARMA: The Dark World</a></em> 