<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-3000-yen-japan-account/13/704a2w?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-5000-yen-japan-account/13/705239?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-9000-yen-japan-account/13/70bkw5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">9,000</a></li></ul><h2><span>Demos, Betas, Updates, etc.</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > 2XKO [13 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/2xko">2XKO</a></em> Closed Beta (PC) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Elden Ring Nightreign [12 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/elden-ring-nightreign">Elden Ring Nightreign</a></em> High-Difficulty Expedition Mode “Deep of Night” (PS5, Xbox Series, PC) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Genshin Impact [128 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/genshin-impact">Genshin Impact</a></em> Version <a title="Platforms > Luna [65 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/cloud/luna">Luna</a> I Update “Song of the Welkin Moon: Segue” (PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, PC, iOS, Android) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Marvel Rivals</em> Season 4: The Heart of the Dragon Update (PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, PC) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Pritto Prisoner [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pritto-prisoner">Pritto Prisoner</a></em> Open Beta (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3036800/PRITTO_PRISONER/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Virtua Fighter 5 R.E.V.O. [5 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/virtua-fighter-5-revo">Virtua Fighter 5 R.E.V.O. World Stage</a></em> Cross-Play Closed Beta Test (PS5, Xbox Series, PC [Steam]) – Launching worldwide.</li></ul></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com